03, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 opening ceremony latest updates  Live updates  We made it!\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1123, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4533092028486016e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four hours of fun in the Paris rain, and now the Olympics are officially underway.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.59594919809561e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The action kicks off early tomorrow morning - join us then as the first medals are won and Team GB look to make a strong start!\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999983406087393, \"rank\": 1.0297702510756314e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that was very special - maybe the loudest cheer of the night for Celine Dion.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.866422065281912e-33, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with that...\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, 