of_Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now it rises up into the sky, hopefully finding a clear path through the rain.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does look incredible.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Charles Coste, who turned 100 earlier this year, holding the torch.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1956, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Coste\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charles Coste\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Coste\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Coste\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won gold at the London Olympics in 1948!\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2043, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999519332, \"rank\": 4.73071947205484e-10, \"text\": \"London Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is the cauldron, with a hot air balloon above it.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former NBA player Tony Parker and Marie-Am\\u00e9lie Le Fur, president of the French Paralympic Committee, among those to join the fun.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999922772688369, \"rank\": 7.668068841677301e-06, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Parker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.2716322069